---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Shipping Policy"
  description="How and when Tacky Turquoise ships, including USPS Ground Advantage timing and tracking."
>
  <section class="policy">
    <div class="policy__inner">
      <div class="policy__crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> &nbsp;/&nbsp; Shipping Policy</div>

      <h1>Shipping <em>Policy.</em></h1>
      <p class="policy__updated">Last updated: 4/25/2026</p>

      <h2>Where We Ship</h2>
      <p>
        We ship within the United States only at this time, including Alaska, Hawaii,
        and US territories.
      </p>

      <h2>How We Ship</h2>
      <p>
        All orders ship via <strong>USPS Ground Advantage</strong> with tracking.
        Shipping cost is calculated at checkout based on the destination — typically
        $5–8 for a single piece.
      </p>
      <p>We use eco-friendly padded mailers or small gift boxes depending on the piece.</p>

      <h2>When We Ship</h2>
      <p>
        Orders are typically shipped within <strong>2–4 business days</strong> of payment.
        We're a small operation — most orders go out within a day or two, but we don't
        ship on weekends or US federal holidays.
      </p>
      <p>You'll receive an email with tracking information as soon as your label is created.</p>

      <h2>Delivery Time</h2>
      <p>
        USPS Ground Advantage typically delivers within
        <strong>2–5 business days</strong> after shipping, depending on destination.
      </p>
      <p>
        Total time from order to delivery is usually about a week. Holiday seasons
        (November–January) and severe weather can extend USPS delivery times — that's
        outside our control.
      </p>

      <h2>Tracking Your Order</h2>
      <p>
        When your order ships, we'll email you a tracking number and a link to USPS
        tracking. You can check status anytime at usps.com.
      </p>

      <h2>Shipping Address</h2>
      <p>
        Please double-check your shipping address before completing checkout. We ship to
        the address provided at checkout exactly as entered. If a package is returned to
        us because of an incorrect address, we'll contact you to arrange reshipment at
        your expense.
      </p>

      <h2>Lost or Damaged Shipments</h2>
      <p>
        If a package is marked as delivered but you didn't receive it, please contact
        USPS to file a claim — once delivery is confirmed, packages are in USPS's and
        your custody.
      </p>
      <p>
        If a piece arrives damaged from shipping, see our
        <a href="/refunds">Refund Policy</a> for how to report it.
      </p>

      <h2>Customs and International</h2>
      <p>
        We don't ship internationally yet. If we expand to international shipping in the
        future, this policy will be updated to cover customs, duties, and timing.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about shipping? Email
        <a href="mailto:orders@tackyturquoise.com">orders@tackyturquoise.com</a>.
      </p>

      <hr />

      <p class="policy__signoff">
        <strong>Apex Quality Analytics LLC</strong>
        DBA Tacky Turquoise<br />
        Olathe, Colorado
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <Footer />
</Base>
